sections.title: Arts, entertainment, and media

* [[Albert (comics)]], a fictional character appearing in comic books published by Marvel Comic
* [[Albert (Discworld)]], a character in Terry Pratchett's ''Discworld'' series

* ''[[Albert the Fifth Musketeer]]'', a 1993 French animated TV series
